import {Component} from 'react'
import { Layout, Menu} from 'antd';

import './tools.less'

const { SubMenu } = Menu;
const { Header, Content, Sider } = Layout;
/*
工具页的路由组件
*/ 
export default class Login extends Component {
  render() {
    return ( 
      <Layout style={{ height: '100%'}}>
        <Header className="header">
          <Menu mode="horizontal" defaultSelectedKeys={['1']}>
            <Menu.Item key="1">收藏夹</Menu.Item>
          </Menu>
        </Header>
        <Layout>
          <Sider width={200} className="tools-sider">
            <Menu mode="inline" style={{ height: '100%'}}
              defaultSelectedKeys={['1']} defaultOpenKeys={['sub1']}
            >
              <SubMenu key="sub1" title="subnav 1">
                <Menu.Item key="1">option1</Menu.Item>
                <Menu.Item key="2">option2</Menu.Item>
                <Menu.Item key="3">option3</Menu.Item>
                <Menu.Item key="4">option4</Menu.Item>
              </SubMenu>
              <SubMenu key="sub2" title="subnav 2">
                <Menu.Item key="5">option1</Menu.Item>
                <Menu.Item key="6">option2</Menu.Item>
                <Menu.Item key="7">option3</Menu.Item>
                <Menu.Item key="8">option4</Menu.Item>
              </SubMenu>
            </Menu>
          </Sider>
          <Layout>
            <Content className="tools-content">
              Content
            </Content>
          </Layout>
        </Layout>
      </Layout>
     );
  }
}
